{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_017HzyLQ2AncR7bZpJCSyCgW","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→package org.quarkus.samples.petclinic.system;\n     2→\n     3→import io.quarkus.qute.i18n.Message;\n     4→import io.quarkus.qute.i18n.MessageBundle;\n     5→\n     6→@MessageBundle\n     7→public interface AppMessages {\n     8→    \n     9→    @Message(\"Find Owner\")\n    10→    String find_owner();\n    11→\n    12→    @Message(\"Last Name\")\n    13→    String last_name();\n    14→\n    15→    @Message(\"Edit Owner\")\n    16→    String edit_owner();\n    17→\n    18→    @Message(\"Add Owner\")\n    19→    String add_owner();\n    20→\n    21→    @Message(\"Find Owners\")\n    22→    String find_owners();\n    23→\n    24→    @Message(\"Name\")\n    25→    String name();\n    26→\n    27→    @Message(\"Address\")\n    28→    String address();\n    29→\n    30→    @Message(\"Telephone\")\n    31→    String telephone();\n    32→\n    33→    @Message(\"City\")\n    34→    String city();\n    35→\n    36→    @Message(\"Pets\")\n    37→    String pets();\n    38→\n    39→    @Message(\"Pet\")\n    40→    String pet();\n    41→\n    42→    @Message(\"Error\")\n    43→    String error();\n    44→\n    45→    @Message(\"None\")\n    46→    String none();\n    47→\n    48→    @Message(\"Veterinarians\")\n    49→    String veterinarians();\n    50→\n    51→    @Message(\"Specialties\")\n    52→    String specialties();\n    53→\n    54→    @Message(\"Welcome\")\n    55→    String welcome();\n    56→\n    57→    @Message(\"Birthdate\")\n    58→    String birthdate();\n    59→\n    60→    @Message(\"Type\")\n    61→    String type();\n    62→\n    63→    @Message(\"Owner\")\n    64→    String owner();\n    65→\n    66→    @Message(\"Edit Pet\")\n    67→    String edit_pet();\n    68→\n    69→    @Message(\"Add Pet\")\n    70→    String add_pet();\n    71→\n    72→    @Message(\"Add Visit\")\n    73→    String add_visit();\n    74→\