{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_01KDtnawzKe7LQdHEM68SDCT","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Now I have a complete understanding of the codebase. This is a Quarkus PetClinic application using:\n- JAX-RS (REST endpoints)\n- Hibernate ORM with Panache (active record pattern)\n- Qute templating engine\n- CDI for dependency injection\n- H2 database for dev/test\n\nI need to migrate to Spring Boot with:\n- Spring MVC (controllers)\n- Spring Data JPA with standard JPA entities\n- Thymeleaf templating (replacing Qute)\n- Spring DI\n- H2 database\n\nLet me mark the analysis as complete and begin the migration."}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":9590,"cache_read_input_tokens":51143,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":9590,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":592},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"d5033181-b1d4-4ac6-8656-753e13eb13fa","uuid":"16a814da-d68a-4666-85fe-986a9b4cca3d"}
