{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_01NNhgRSmHa1KaR93KTCormN","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Now I need to think about the Thymeleaf template layout strategy. The `base.html` uses `th:insert=\"~{:: #body-content}\"` which means each page should have its content in a `div id=\"body-content\"`. But the approach I used requires a different mechanism. Let me reconsider - in Thymeleaf, the simplest approach for layout is to use `th:replace` with fragments, or to use a separate layout approach. Let me use a simpler direct approach where each template is self-contained with the base layout inlined via Thymeleaf's `th:fragment` and `th:replace` mechanism.\n\nActually, the cleanest approach for this migration is to use Thymeleaf Layout Dialect or just inline the base layout in each template. But the simplest approach that works without additional dependencies is to have each page as a standalone HTML that extends the layout using `th:replace`/`th:insert` fragments.\n\nLet me reconsider the template strategy. The most straightforward Thymeleaf approach without a layout dialect is to use fragments. Let me rewrite the templates properly:"}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":2336,"cache_read_input_tokens":102571,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":2336,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":2006},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"d5033181-b1d4-4ac6-8656-753e13eb13fa","uuid":"1fd87476-e0ad-47ac-8694-e2eb6bce78f9"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_01NNhgRSmHa1KaR93KTCormN","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_bdrk_0139KocHZLcLuEwJQnYg3bhP","name":"Bash","input":{"command":"cd /home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__quarkus__spring/run_3/output\n\n# base.html is a layout fragment that other templates insert into\ncat > src/main/resources/templates/fragments/layout.html << 'TEMPLATE_EOF'\n<!doctype html>\n<html xmlns:th=\"http://www.thymeleaf.org\" th:fragment=\"layout(content)\">\n\n<head>\n  <meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\" />\n  <meta charset=\"utf-8\">\n  <meta http-equiv=\"X-UA-Compatible\" content=\"IE=edge\">\n  <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1\">\n  <title>PetClinic :: a Spring Boot Framework demonstration</title>\n  <link rel=\"shortcut icon\" type=\"image/x-icon\" th:href=\"@{/images/favicon.ico}\">\n  <link rel=\"stylesheet\" th:href=\"@{/webjars/font-awesome/4.7.0/css/font-awesome.min.css}\">\n  <link rel=\"stylesheet\" th:href=\"@{/css/petclinic.css}\" />\n</head>\n\n<body>\n  <nav class=\"navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-dark\" role=\"navigation\">\n    <div class=\"container\">\n      <div class=\"navbar-header\">\n        <a class=\"navbar-brand\" th:href=\"@{/}\"><span></span></a>\n        <button class=\"navbar-toggler\" type=\"button\" data-bs-toggle=\"collapse\" data-bs-target=\"#main-navbar\">\n          <span class=\"navbar-toggler-icon\"></span>\n        </button>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"collapse navbar-collapse\" id=\"main-navbar\" style>\n        <ul class=\"nav navbar-nav me-auto\">\n          <li class=\"active\">\n            <a th:href=\"@{/}\" title=\"home page\">\n              <span class=\"fa fa-home\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span>\n              <span>Home</span>\n            </a>\n          </li>\n          <li>\n            <a th:href=\"@{/owners/find}\" title=\"find owners\">\n              <span class=\"fa fa-search\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span>\n              <span>Find Owners</span>\n            </a>\n          </li>\n          <li>\n            <a th:href=\"@{/vets.html}\" title=\"veterinarians\">\n              <span class=\"fa fa-th-list\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span>\n              <span>Veterinarians</span>\n            </a>\n          </li>\n          <li>\n            <a th:href=\"@{/oups}\" title=\"trigger a RuntimeException to see how it is handled\">\n              <span class=\"fa exclamation-triangle\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span>\n              <span>Error</span>\n            </a>\n          </li>\n        </ul>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </nav>\n  <div class=\"container-fluid\">\n    <div class=\"container xd-container\">\n      <div th:replace=\"${content}\">\n        No body!\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <script th:src=\"@{/webjars/bootstrap/5.1.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js}\"></script>\n</body>\n\n</html>\nTEMPLATE_EOF\n\necho \"layout.html created\"\n\n# Now rewrite all templates to use the layout\ncat > src/main/resources/templates/welcome.html << 'TEMPLATE_EOF'\n<!doctype html>\n<html xmlns:th=\"http://www.thymeleaf.org\" th:replace=\"~{fragments/layout :: layout(~{:: #body-content})}\">\n<body>\n<div id=\"body-content\">\n  <h2>Welcome</h2>\n  <div class=\"row\">\n      <div class=\"col-md-12\">\n        <img class=\"img-responsive\" th:src=\"@{/images/pets.png}\"/>\n      </div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\nTEMPLATE_EOF\n\ncat > src/main/resources/templates/error.html << 'TEMPLATE_EOF'\n<!doctype html>\n<html xmlns:th=\"http://www.thymeleaf.org\" th:replace=\"~{fragments/layout :: layout(~{:: #body-content})}\">\n<body>\n<div id=\"body-content\">\n  <h2>Welcome</h2>\n  <div class=\"row\">\n      <div class=\"col-md-12\">\n        <img class=\"img-responsive\" th:src=\"@{/images/pets.png}\"/>\n        <h2>Error</h2>\n        <p>Something happened...</p>\n        <p th:if=\"${message != null}\" th:text=\"${message}\">Error message</p>\n      </div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\nTEMPLATE_EOF\n\ncat > src/main/resources/templates/findOwners.html << 'TEMPLATE_EOF'\n<!doctype html>\n<html xmlns:th=\"http://www.thymeleaf.org\" th:replace=\"~{fragments/layout :: layout(~{:: #body-content})}\">\n<body>\n<div id=\"body-content\">\n  <h2>Find Owners</h2>\n  <form action=\"/owners\" method=\"get\" class=\"form-horizontal\" id=\"search-owner-form\">\n    <div class=\"form-group\">\n      <div class=\"control-group\" id=\"lastNameGroup\">\n        <label class=\"col-sm-2 control-label\">Last Name</label>\n        <div class=\"col-sm-10\">\n          <input type=\"text\" class=\"form-control\" id=\"lastName\" name=\"lastName\" size=\"30\" maxlength=\"80\" />\n          <div th:if=\"${errors != null and !errors.isEmpty()}\">\n            <span class=\"help-inline\">\n              <div>\n                <p th:each=\"err : ${errors}\" th:text=\"${err}\"></p>\n              </div>\n            </span>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"form-group\">\n      <div class=\"col-sm-offset-2 col-sm-10\">\n        <button type=\"submit\" class=\"btn btn-primary\">Find Owner</button>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <a class=\"btn btn-primary\" th:href=\"@{/owners/new}\">Add Owner</a>\n  </form>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\nTEMPLATE_EOF\n\necho \"Templates batch 1 done\"","description":"Rewrite templates with layout pattern"}}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":2336,"cache_read_input_tokens":102571,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":2336,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":2006},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"d5033181-b1d4-4ac6-8656-753e13eb13fa","uuid":"b87082ff-af3a-443e-8592-a592f5f57e7a"}
