{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_01WBKRj3MFeGyKnLc8ZFLZ4o","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Migration complete. Here is the final report:\n\n---\n\n### Migration Summary\n\n- **Frameworks:** Quarkus 3.30.5 → Spring Boot 3.2.5\n- **High-level actions:** Replaced all Quarkus dependencies with Spring Boot equivalents, rewrote all JAX-RS endpoints as Spring MVC controllers, converted Panache entities to standard JPA with Spring Data repositories, migrated Qute templates to Thymeleaf, moved static resources, updated Dockerfile\n- **Overall outcome:** **Success** - All 14 smoke tests pass, application builds and runs correctly\n\n### File Tree\n\n```\nModified:\n- pom.xml: Replaced Quarkus dependencies with Spring Boot 3.2.5\n- Dockerfile: Updated build/run commands for Spring Boot fat JAR\n- src/main/resources/application.properties: Migrated to Spring Boot config format\n- src/main/resources/templates/*.html: Converted from Qute to Thymeleaf (10 files)\n\nAdded:\n- src/main/java/org/springframework/samples/petclinic/PetClinicApplication.java: Spring Boot main class\n- src/main/java/.../model/Person.java: Base entity (standard JPA)\n- src/main/java/.../owner/Owner.java: Owner entity\n- src/main/java/.../owner/Pet.java: Pet entity\n- src/main/java/.../owner/PetType.java: PetType entity\n- src/main/java/.../owner/OwnerRepository.java: Spring Data JPA repository\n- src/main/java/.../owner/PetRepository.java: Spring Data JPA repository\n- src/main/java/.../owner/PetTypeRepository.java: Spring Data JPA repository\n- src/main/java/.../owner/OwnerController.java: Spring MVC controller\n- src/main/java/.../owner/PetController.java: Spring MVC controller\n- src/main/java/.../owner/VisitController.java: Spring MVC controller\n- src/main/java/.../vet/Specialty.java: Specialty entity\n- src/main/java/.../vet/Vet.java: Vet entity\n- src/main/java/.../vet/Vets.java: Vets DTO\n- src/main/java/.../vet/VetRepository.java: Spring Data JPA repository\n- src/main/java/.../vet/VetController.java: Spring MVC controller\n- src/main/java/.../visit/Visit.java: Visit entity\n- src/main/java/.../visit/VisitRepository.java: Spring Data JPA repository\n- src/main/java/.../system/WelcomeController.java: Welcome page controller\n- src/main/java/.../system/CrashController.java: Error trigger controller\n- src/main/java/.../system/ErrorController.java: Global exception handler\n- src/main/resources/templates/fragments/layout.html: Thymeleaf layout fragment\n- src/main/resources/static/css/petclinic.css: Minimal CSS\n- src/main/resources/static/ (images, fonts copied from META-INF/resources)\n- src/main/resources/data.sql: Seed data (Spring Boot convention)\n- smoke.py: 14 smoke tests\n- CHANGELOG.md: Migration documentation\n\nRemoved:\n- src/main/java/org/quarkus/ (entire old package tree - 21 Java files)\n- src/test/java/org/quarkus/ (old test files)\n- src/main/docker/ (Quarkus-specific Dockerfiles)\n- src/main/resources/import.sql (replaced by data.sql)\n```\n\n### Error Handling\n\n- **Error Summary:** 1 error encountered, 0 unresolved\n- **Error:** Duplicate key violation at startup caused by both Hibernate's `import.sql` and Spring's `data.sql` loading seed data simultaneously\n  - **Resolution:** Removed `import.sql`, kept only `data.sql` with `spring.jpa.defer-datasource-initialization=true`\n- **No critical or unresolved issues**"}],"stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":540,"cache_read_input_tokens":153151,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":540,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":991},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"d5033181-b1d4-4ac6-8656-753e13eb13fa","uuid":"721f6270-2826-496b-a914-c00d1ee27600"}
